game.objects

Class AbstractObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.objects.AbstractObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ball, Bomb, ColorArea, ColorBar

    public abstract class AbstractObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Class has the common properties of all the objects in game. All the objects are round. Has the basic vector logic for moving to certain direction andlogic for drawing the image.
    Author:
    esa
